{"tid":911661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自殺炸彈客坐他前面　實錄恐怖爆炸瞬間血肉橫飛","createTime":"2018-11-22T05:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T06:28:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"44e6c7a9e0eb7a5558e02cb70a148c0448ebd7e8","tid":911661,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"阿富汗首都喀布爾一個大型宴會廳，周二發生自殺式炸彈襲擊，造成逾50人死亡、超過90人受傷，而現場有民眾剛好錄下恐怖的爆炸瞬間。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，11月20日是伊斯蘭教三大節日之一的「聖紀節」，穆斯林在此日紀念先知穆罕默德的誕辰。這處宴會廳剛好舉辦慶祝「聖紀節」的活動，現場有許多伊斯蘭教學者和神職人員參加。其中一名參加民眾，拿出手機錄下宴會廳裡的場景，原本只聽到司儀的念經祝禱聲，過不久，鏡頭突然發出「砰」的一聲，並拍到熊熊火光，原來這個鏡頭，剛好拍下自殺炸彈客啟動爆炸的瞬間。<br />\n畫面更可見，就在爆炸後的剎那，一名死者遺體就飛到鏡頭前，接著拍攝者就追隨人群，趕緊逃走。一名生還者法理德(Ahmad Fareed)接受媒體訪問時說：「我的朋友和小兒子坐在我旁邊，全身都是血，動彈不得。」、「現場真的非常恐怖，一堆死者與傷患，血肉橫飛。」<br />\n當地官員指出，一名自殺炸彈客在大廳內引爆炸彈，目前沒有組織承認責任，而死傷者多集中在宴會廳的前方位置。過往塔利班和當地的伊斯蘭恐怖組織分支，一直針對親政府的宗教學者發動攻擊。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_c155488ca8f1a2f5cd097289e28de8e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_c155488ca8f1a2f5cd097289e28de8e5.jpg&h=ee467861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_be7f0823e3a0e6372c27c0a2bdb4346f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_be7f0823e3a0e6372c27c0a2bdb4346f.jpg&h=76180a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_444ccafafa477e5425a570b2bf7de258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_444ccafafa477e5425a570b2bf7de258.jpg&h=d3b15fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_5b5ed9c447ea884842edae3484cb2b38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_5b5ed9c447ea884842edae3484cb2b38.jpg&h=9b5e7fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_55dd45d4658c0afd89aea69a6ca7ef7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_55dd45d4658c0afd89aea69a6ca7ef7c.jpg&h=0d4991fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181122/1470989/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181122%2F1470989%2F&d=dfeeB01biWcpSatpjJUPM7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2c7f4e39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181122%2F1470989%2F&h=c1a44202\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181122/1470989/</a>"},{"pid":"e5d7a981a6084d04d40a9aedce676b96f500c537","tid":911661,"uid":11148,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"見到topic即刻衝入黎,因為知道實有圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85448661dd8e4e77a095eaa6acb560553069f5e9","tid":911661,"uid":52148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"估中有圖"},{"pid":"855a3f77dfbc5a940a99db8c180e657241e90564","tid":911661,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"變炸醬"},{"pid":"2323a206ac0dd493c45a5df100e38024ccb8eaee","tid":911661,"uid":209079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T06:24:14.000Z","msg":"41j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab2e99222b475ac972d0fd6fee117b88da5d6a3","tid":911661,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"呢D就高清"},{"pid":"c84f5ba67807646aafb8aca2ba8b62714208165f","tid":911661,"uid"